@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gcahss(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.49 * v2 + 0.94)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((tmp + 0.17 + v2 + 0.45)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.04) + v0) + (0.59 / v1))
    v2 = ((v0 / v2) / ((v0 + 0.13 / tmp + 0.91) + (v0 + 1.00 / v0 + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
